istory to [[Vietnam]] before meeting one of the religious gathering participants where he was being hospitalised in Kuala Lumpur and another was a 69-year-old man gathering participant from [[Kelantan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/03/21/sarawak-independently-reports-two-more-covid-19-deaths/1848758|title=Sarawak independently reports two more Covid-19 deaths|last=Tawie|first=Sulok|work=The Malay Mail|date=21 March 2020|accessdate=21 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321093731/https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/03/21/sarawak-independently-reports-two-more-covid-19-deaths/1848758|archive-date=21 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/74884/KHAS/Koronavirus/Malaysia-catat-lima-kematian-baharu-1.74884|title=Malaysia catat lima kematian baharu|trans-title=Malaysia recorded five new deaths|last=Abu Hassan|first=Mohd Ridzuan|language=Malay|work=Sinar Harian|date=21 March 2020|accessdate=21 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321111547/https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/74884/KHAS/Koronavirus/Malaysia-catat-lima-kematian-baharu-1.74884|archive-date=21 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://says.com/my/news/8-m-sians-have-died-from-covid-19-as-dr-noor-hisham-warns-of-a-rise-in-new-cases-next-week|title=8 M'sians Have Died From COVID-19 As Dr Noor Hisham Warns Of A Rise In New Cases Next Week|last=Ram|first=Sadho|work=Says.com|date=21 March 2020|accessdate=21 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321114313/https://says.com/my/news/8-m-sians-have-died-from-covid-19-as-dr-noor-hisham-warns-of-a-rise-in-new-cases-next-week|archive-date=21 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> A total of six Malaysian police officers also have been infected by the virus while serving their duty.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/enam-anggota-pdrm-positif-covid-19-335-anggota-masih-tunggu-